HTML-Doctype
============

Fun stuff with document type declarations in HTML / XHTML / XML
documents.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  SGML::Parser::OpenSP;

